<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.4">
<l>veṉṟicēr tiṇmai vilaṅkalmā mēṉi veḷḷeyiṟ ṟoḷḷerit taṟukaṇ</l>
<l>paṉṟiyā yaṉṟu pārmakaḷ payalai tīrttavaṉ pañcavar pākaṉ</l>
<l>oṉṟalā vuruvat tulappilpal  kālat tuyarkoṭi yoḷivaḷar matiyam</l>
<l>ceṉṟucēr ceṉṉic cikaranaṉ māṭat tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The charioteer for the Five, the one who removed the pallor</l>
<l rend="indent">of lady earth long ago as a boar</l>
<l>With bright, burning, cruel eyes [and] white tusks,</l>
<l rend="indent">his huge body [like] a mountain, strong in victory,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi, [its] fine mansions with spires on top</l>
<l rend="indent">which reaches the bright waxing moon</l>
<l>[And] banners of not [just] one shape,</l>
<l rend="indent">raised for many seasons without tattering.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
